        <updateDate>2021-05-03T14:36:57Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Save America's Clean Energy Jobs Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows taxpayers to receive direct payments of amounts relating to the tax credit for the production of electricity from renewable resources, the energy tax credit, and the carbon oxide sequestration tax credit in lieu of such credits.</p>]]>
        </text>
